  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3136686/" class="title-link">日本粪青史话</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3136686"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/taxiliya/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1520068-19.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/taxiliya/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">风起湘江</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-04-02"
      class="main-meta">2010-04-02 15:13:52</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3136686_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这个就是我写的，转载什么的，耍你们的！  20世纪初日本走向法西斯主义和军国主义的历史，偶的体会，可以归纳成两条路线的斗争：愤青路线和非愤青路线的斗争。说得学术点，就是极端民族主义和国际协调主义，说得中国化一点，就是“爱”国主义和“卖”国主义的斗争。日本愤青这...

